'''飓风莎瑞'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Shary}}）是2010年10月一直在北大西洋开放海域上空活动的一场持续时间较为短暂的[[北大西洋热带气旋|热带气旋]]。系统源于中大西洋上空的弱[[对流|对流]]区，于10月28日达到热带风暴强度，成为[[2010年大西洋飓风季|2010年大西洋飓风季]]第18场获得命名的风暴。气象机构起初预测莎瑞的风速不会超过每小时85公里，但气旋实际上却于10月30日从[[百慕大|百慕大]]以东较远处洋面经过期间达到飓风的最低标准，成为本季第11场飓风。由于外界环境不利，风暴很快开始失去热带天气系统特征，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]于当晚发布最后一份公告，宣布莎瑞已退化成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。

气旋对陆地产生的影响很小，百慕大降下小雨，岛上的阵风时速即便是在风暴距离最近时也没有超过55公里。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Shary 2010 track.png}}
2010年10月下旬，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]开始对一片[[锋_(气象)|锋面系统]]南部边缘沿线的弱天气区进行监控，这片组织混乱的天气区还同[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]东北偏东方向一片广阔的[[低压槽|表面槽]]相互关联<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL202010_Shary.pdf | archivedate = 2013-05-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130531014051/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL202010_Shary.pdf | deadurl = yes | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author = Lixion A. Avila | date = 2011-01-03 | accessdate = 2013-05-31 | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | title = Hurricane SHARY Tropical Cyclone Report}}</ref>。受西南方向逐渐减退的[[冷心低压|上层低气压]]影响，系统断断续续地产生时而密集时而稀疏的[[对流|对流]]，引发局部[[雷暴|雷暴]]和降雨<ref>{{cite report | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2010-10-27 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author1 = Pasch | author2 = Kimberlain}}</ref>。由于系统行经海域环境渐趋有利，对流活动也逐渐增强<ref>{{cite report | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2010-10-28 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author1 = Blake | author2 = Brown}}</ref>。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]10月28日中午12点左右，[[气象卫星|卫星图像]]显示低压槽内似乎有[[低气压|下层低气压]]形成，美国国家飓风中心认为系统有很大可能会发展成[[热带气旋|热带]]或[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-12-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141219040020/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201010281137/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201010281137 | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2010-10-28 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201010281137/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201010281137 | author1 = Blake | deadurl = no | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Brown}}</ref>。环流中心这时仍然很混乱，但到这天晚上已经有所改善，并包含有一定的对流<ref>{{cite web | author1 = Brown | author2 = Berg | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141219040028/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201010282347/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201010282347 | date = 2010-10-28 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201010282347/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201010282347 | deadurl = no | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | archivedate = 2014-12-19}}</ref>。由于系统的[[最大风速半径|风力半径]]很小，因此上层低气压虽然仍在左近，但已在风力半径的西南方向以外，这种结构在亚热带气旋中非常少见<ref name="discuss001">{{cite report | author1 = Brown | author2 = Berg | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2010-10-29 | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | title = Tropical Storm Shary Discussion One | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141221085413/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.discus.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.discus.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-12-21 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。美国国家飓风中心因此于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}10月29日凌晨0点将系统归类为热带风暴并以“莎瑞”（{{lang|en|Shary}}）命名，但经过飓风季过后的重新分析，该机构确认{{lang|en|UTC}}10月28日下午18点时，[[百慕大|百慕大]]东南偏南方向约830公里洋面就已形成热带低气压<ref name="public001">{{cite report | author1 = Brown | author2 = Berg | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2010-10-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102223312/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.public.001.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | title = Tropical Storm Shary Public Advisory One | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.public.001.shtml?}}</ref><ref name="TCR" />。美国国家飓风中心还在为风暴命名的同时指出，气旋的持续时间不长，会在48小时内与[[冷锋|冷锋]]合并<ref name="discuss001" />。

[[File:Tropical_Storm_Shary_2010-10-29_1520Z.jpg|thumb]]

受上层低气压和东北方向的中层[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响，莎瑞在两者间转向西北方向移动，系统逐渐同上层低气压分离，云层格局变得更加规则。次日清晨，虽然中心仍然部分暴露在外，但对流已经在西侧半圆内稳步深化<ref name="discuss002">{{cite report | author1 = Blake | author2 = Brennan | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103030439/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.discus.002.shtml | date = 2010-10-29 | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | title = Tropical Storm Shary Discussion Two | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.discus.002.shtml?}}</ref>。但随着风暴移动至上层低气压北侧，气旋上空的北向[[风切变|风切变]]增多，内部核心中的对流也移动到中心以南。随着莎瑞的前进速度大幅放缓，干燥空气开始把风暴的东部和东北部象限包裹起来，对流因此受到一定程度的侵蚀<ref name="discuss003">{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103015249/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.discus.003.shtml | author = Stacy Stewart | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2010-10-29 | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | title = Tropical Storm Shary Discussion Three | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.discus.003.shtml? | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-01-03}}</ref>。由于上层低气压的影响逐渐减小，风暴恢复蜿蜒北上的前进方向，气象机构预计，由于高空大气环境只有小幅改善，因此莎瑞的强度也只会出现小幅回升。但是，有多个[[热带气旋预测模型|预测模型]]认为气旋会在36小时内达到飓风标准，美国国家飓风中心对此表示，由于风切变非常强，[[海面温度|海面温度]]也很低，莎瑞基本上不可能达到飓风强度。<ref name="discuss002" /><ref name="discuss003" />然而，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机测得的数据表明气旋的[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]逐渐走高，最低中心气压也在降低，对流于当晚再度爆发并迅速在东面扩张开来<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Roberts | author2 = Brown | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2010-10-29 | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | title = Tropical Storm Shary Discussion Five | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103035506/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.discus.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.discus.005.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-01-03}}</ref>。当天深夜，雷暴活动进一步强化，中心附近对流也均匀对称地深化，从微波图像上还可以看到很小的[[风眼|眼状特征]]发展出来。虽然[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克分析法]]获得的结果还远远没有达到飓风强度标准，但莎瑞还是在10月30日以风力时速120公里强度被升级成[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|一级飓风]]，多位专家称，风暴的规模非常小，如果没有微波卫星图像根本无法发现。达到这一强度时，莎瑞已经盘距在深层西南向中纬度气流内，并因此加速向东北方向前进<ref>{{cite report | author = Eric Blake | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2010-10-30 | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | title = Hurricane Shary Discussion Six | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.discus.006.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103024133/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.discus.006.shtml | archivedate = 2014-01-03}}</ref>。

飓风继续加速移动，行经洋面水温逐渐降低，其西侧不远处还有强劲的冷锋。莎瑞的对流逐渐变得不对称，但微小的风眼在微波图像上仍然清晰可见。<ref>{{cite report | author = John Cangialosi | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2010-10-30 | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | title = Hurricane Shary Discussion Seven | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025031319/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.discus.007.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.discus.007.shtml? | deadurl = no}}</ref>短短几小时内，气旋同冷锋迅速发生相互影响，表明风暴正在向温带气旋转变。气旋[[相空间|相空间图]]的数据表明，莎瑞最终是在[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]][[开普雷斯|开普雷斯]]（{{lang|en|Cape Race}}）[[罗盘方位|东南偏南]]方向约885公里洋面完全转变成温带气旋，美国国家飓风中心随即停止发布公告<ref>{{cite report | author = John Cangialosi | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2010-10-30 | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.discus.008.shtml? | deadurl = no | title = Tropical Storm Shary Discussion Eight | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025031344/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.discus.008.shtml}}</ref>。当晚，飓风莎瑞的温带残留完全被邻近的冷锋吸收<ref name="TCR" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
10月28日，美国国家飓风中心针对莎瑞发布首份公告，百慕大政府随后立即向全岛发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]<ref name="public001" />。[[捷蓝航空|捷蓝航空]]因风暴而取消多架从美国飞往百慕大的航班<ref name="ff" />。连接[[圣大卫岛|圣大卫岛]]和百慕大主岛的低洼堤道安排在当地时间10月29日晚上19点关闭，另外还有多场球赛因此取消<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102192725/http://bernews.com/2010/10/causeway-to-close-at-7pm-tonight/ | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | url = http://bernews.com/2010/10/causeway-to-close-at-7pm-tonight/ | title = Causeway To Close at 7pm Tonight | date = 2010-10-29 | publisher = Bernews | author = Staff Writer | accessdate = 2015-10-04}}</ref>。[[哈密尔顿教区|哈密尔顿教区]]到[[圣乔治岛|圣乔治岛]]之间的轮渡服务暂时中止<ref name="ff">{{cite web |author=Staff Writer |publisher=Go Jamaica |date=2010-10-29 |accessdate=2015-10-04 |title=Flights and ferry service canceled as Tropical Storm Shary heads for Bermuda |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5ts1JCvgG?url=http://go-jamaica.com/news/read_article.php?id=23786 |url=http://jamaica-gleaner.com/power/23786 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2010-10-30 }}</ref>。地方官员敦促居民稳固船只，以防万一<ref>{{cite web | author = Elizabeth Roberts | publisher = The Houston Chronicle | date = 2010-10-29 | accessdate = 2010-10-31 | title = Tropical Storm Shary approaches Bermuda | archivedate = 2010-10-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101031174737/http://www.chron.com/disp/story.mpl/ap/top/all/7270749.html | url = http://www.chron.com/disp/story.mpl/ap/top/all/7270749.html | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。10月29日，由于气旋已不再对百慕大构成威胁，之前发布的热带风暴警告相应取消<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Roberts | author2 = Brown | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103030602/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.public.005.shtml | deadurl = no | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2010-10-29 | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | title = Tropical Storm Shary Public Advisory Five | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al20/al202010.public.005.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-01-03}}</ref>。

莎瑞尚未[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]百慕大就已转向，因此对岛上产生的影响很小。风暴期间岛上降雨量仅有14毫米，阵风时速也没有超过55公里。<ref>{{cite web |publisher=Bermuda Weather Service |date=2010-10-30 |accessdate=2010-10-30 |title=Daily Climatology Written Summary: October 1, 2010 to October 29, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2010-10-30 |url=http://www.weather.bm/climatereport/climateReport.asp |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5ts0XUxXr?url=http://www.weather.bm/climatereport/climateReport.asp }}</ref>

